Learn how your dog&#039;s mind works. Cesar Millan&#039;s Dog Whisperer uses interactive 
games to teach Millan&#039;s world-renowned methodology and help owners understand 
their dogs. You are confronted with 40 different common dog issues and, using 
Cesar Millan&#039;s guidance, learn how to deal with each of them.
